"title": "5828: danger",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5828: danger",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A condition of threat, physical or spiritual, in which evil, malice, accident or destruction looms.</p>\n<h2>Physical danger</h2>\n<h3>In nature</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:23\">LUK 8:23</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:24\">MAT 8:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:37\">MRK 4:37</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:11-1Kgs19:12\">1KI 19:11–19:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps83:14-Ps83:15\">PSA 83:14–83:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:23-Ps107:28\">PSA 107:23–107:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:26-Acts16:30\">ACT 16:26–16:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:26\">2CO 11:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:13\">REV 11:13</a></p>\n<h3>From human violence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps140:1\">PSA 140:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen27:41-Gen27:43\">GEN 27:41–27:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod2:15\">EXO 2:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:1-1Sam19:2\">1SA 19:1–19:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:3\">2SA 22:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:1-1Kgs19:3\">1KI 19:1–19:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:7-Neh4:9\">NEH 4:7–4:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps7:9\">PSA 7:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps64:1\">PSA 64:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:20\">PSA 74:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:5\">ECC 12:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:28-Luke4:29\">LUK 4:28–4:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:35\">ACT 21:35</a></p>\n<h3>Through foolishness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:3\">PRO 22:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:12\">PRO 27:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:13-Eccl2:14\">ECC 2:13–2:14</a></p>\n<h2>Spiritual danger</h2>\n<h3>From the devil</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:8\">1PE 5:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:1-Gen3:5\">GEN 3:1–3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:6-Job1:12\">JOB 1:6–1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:1-Job2:6\">JOB 2:1–2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:1-Matt4:11\">MAT 4:1–4:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:2-Luke4:13\">LUK 4:2–4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:2\">JHN 13:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:14\">HEB 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:8\">1JN 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:10\">REV 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:10\">REV 20:10</a></p>\n<h3>Danger of hell through disobedience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:22\">MAT 5:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:4-Luke12:5\">LUK 12:4–12:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:4-1Cor5:5\">1CO 5:4–5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:4-Heb6:6\">HEB 6:4–6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:4-2Pet2:10\">2PE 2:4–2:10</a></p>\n<h3>Danger of loss through unfaithfulness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:13-1Cor3:15\">1CO 3:13–3:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:21\">ROM 6:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:21\">ROM 6:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:26-1Cor9:27\">1CO 9:26–9:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:9-1Tim6:10\">1TI 6:9–6:10</a></p>\n<h3>Danger does not overcome the faithful</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:35\">ROM 8:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:10-2Tim3:11\">2TI 3:10–3:11</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of those endangered</h2>\n<h3>Israel by her enemies</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:17-Exod13:22\">EXO 13:17–13:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth3:1-Esth3:6\">EST 3:1–3:6</a></p>\n<h3>Joseph, through betrayal</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:18-Gen37:28\">GEN 37:18–37:28</a></p>\n<h3>Prophets, because of persecution</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:1-Jer38:11\">JER 38:1–38:11</a></p>\n<h3>Jonah, through disobedience</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah1:4-Jonah1:17\">JON 1:4–1:17</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ, through betrayal</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:3-Matt26:4\">MAT 26:3–26:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:14-Matt26:16\">MAT 26:14–26:16</a></p>\n<h3>Paul, through shipwreck</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:13-Acts27:20\">ACT 27:13–27:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:42-Acts27:44\">ACT 27:42–27:44</a></p>",
